<tr>
<th colspan="2" style="text-align:center; background:#6699FF; padding:0.2em; line-height:1.2em;">Holding</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center; padding:0; line-height:1.2em; vertical-align:middle;">The <a href="/wiki/Fifth_Amendment_to_the_United_States_Constitution" title="Fifth Amendment to the United States Constitution">Fifth Amendment</a> privilege against self-incrimination requires law enforcement officials to advise a suspect interrogated in custody of his rights to remain silent and to obtain an attorney. Arizona Supreme Court reversed and remanded.</td>
</tr>
